Package org.rdkit.knime.types

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RDKitMolValue
    Smiles Data Value interface.
    RDKitReactionValue
    Smiles Data Value interface.
    RDKitTypeConversionErrorListener
    This interface can be implemented by classes interested in receiving information about conversion errors that occur when a type converter is auto-converting data cells.
    RDKitTypeConversionErrorProvider
    This interface gets implemented by type converters that support that listeners can be attached to be informed about conversion errors.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RDKitAdapterCell
    An RDKit Adapter Cell combines multiple chemical molecule value representations in one cell.
    RDKitAdapterCell.RDKitAdapterCellSerializer
    Serializer for RDKitAdapterCells.
    RDKitCountBasedFingerprintDeserializer
    Deserializer implementation for converting Python RDKit count-based fingerprint types UIntSparseIntVect, IntSparseIntVect and LongSparseIntVect into KNIME Fingerprint cells.
    RDKitCountBasedFingerprintDeserializer.Factory
    Factory class for creating the RDKitFingerprintDeserializer
    RDKitFingerprintDeserializer
    Deserializer implementation for converting Python RDKit ExplicitBitVect type into KNIME Fingerprint cells.
    RDKitFingerprintDeserializer.Factory
    Factory class for creating the RDKitFingerprintDeserializer
    RDKitMolCell2
    Implementation of an RDKit Molecule Cell.
    RDKitMolCell2.RDKitSerializer
    Factory for (de-)serializing a RDKitMolCell.
    RDKitMolCellFactory
    Factory creating RDKitMolValue compatible DataCell objects.
    RDKitMolDeserializer
    Deserializer implementation for converting Python RDKit Molecules into RDKit Mol Cells.
    RDKitMolDeserializer.Factory
    Factory class for creating the RDKitMolDeserializer
    RDKitMolSerializer
    Serializer implementation for converting RDKit Mol Cells into exchange format for Python code.
    RDKitMolSerializer.Factory
    Factory class for creating the RDKitMolSerializer
    RDKitMolValue.RDKUtilityFactory
    Implementations of the meta information of this value class.
    RDKitMolValueRenderer
    This a renderer that draws nice 2D depictions of RDKit molecules.
    RDKitMolValueRenderer.Factory
    Factory for RDKitMolValueRenderer.
    RDKitReactionCell  
    RDKitReactionCell.RDKitReactionSerializer
    Factory for (de-)serializing a RDKitMolCell.
    RDKitReactionDeserializer
    Deserializer implementation for converting Python ChemicalReaction type into RDKit Chemical Reaction cells.
    RDKitReactionDeserializer.Factory
    Factory class for creating the RDKitMolDeserializer
    RDKitReactionSerializer
    Serializer implementation for converting RDKit Chemical Reaction Cells into exchange format for Python code.
    RDKitReactionSerializer.Factory
    Factory class for creating the RDKitReactionSerializer
    RDKitReactionValue.RDKUtilityFactory
    Implementations of the meta information of this value class.
    RDKitTypeConverter
    Converter for RDKit that converts Smiles or SDF cells into an adapter cell that contains RDKit cells.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RDKitTypeConverterException
    This runtime exception gets thrown when conversion of a SMILES or SDF value into an RDKitMolValue for an Adapter Cell fails.
